 with spatula."},{"content":"Add drinking chocolate and cream alternative then whip <b>20 sec\/speed 6<b>. Divide mousse between 8 serving glasses and crumble over cooled chocolate cake to look like soil. Arrange jelly worms on crumbled cake and serve immediately or chill until needed."}],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","3h","8 portions"]}